JOB PURPOSE 
============================================== 
 
Help us build intuitive user interfaces that delight our users and help them solve real-world problems. Use your top-notch UI skills to innovate with us and create the next generation of industrial AI enabled products.
 
 
The Artificial Intelligence (AI) team works with teams across the business to promote AI and develop AI content. This role is a member of the AI team who works with UX designers, data scientists, system developers and product managers to create modern, visually appealing user interfaces for prototypes and production software for on premises and cloud-based solutions.
 
 
 Present complex information in an easily digestible format
 Support streamlined data interactions and exploration
 Drive a common experience across multiple products
 Cloud-first, responsive browser-based development
 
DESCRIPTION 
============================================== 
 
This role is responsible for creating interactive front ends for AI software. Activities include working with stakeholders to understand and refine UX requirements and workflows to create designs and prototypes for user testing; working with systems developers to define and refine appropriate API interfaces and then coding and verifying user interfaces for AI products. Developers in this role will create rapid protypes and demonstrations by stubbing or simulating back-end services as required.
 
 
The ideal candidate will be an expert in creating dynamic, interactive, intuitive, and professional HTML-based user interfaces for AI applications. These applications will focus around data, so the developer should be skilled in the different ways of displaying and interacting with data including interactive charting, data navigation, exploration and manipulation.
 
 
The candidate will work with different product teams to aid in integrating AI modules into different products. The primary focus will be on cloud-based applications, with some additional work for traditional, on-premises applications.
 
 
PRINCIPAL RESPONSIBILITIES 
============================================== 
 
 Create best in class interactive front ends for AI software
 Develop prototypes and proof of concept software to verify concepts
 Verify UI through manual and automated testing
 Work with the UI / UX team to identify and adopt UI tools and standards
 Develop UI for batch & real-time analytical solutions, prototypes, and proofs of concept for selected solutions.
 Implement UI for analytical projects with a focus on collecting, managing, analysing, and visualising data.
 Be in constant communication with team members, stakeholders and other relevant parties and collaborate on first class user experiences.
 Support and mentor other developers who want to become UI / UX developers
 Create UI conventions and standards and mentor others in their adoption 
 
 
IMPORTANT WORKING RELATIONSHIPS 
============================================== 
 
 Business stakeholders
 AI Engineers
 Software development teams
 UI / UX team 
 
 
KNOWLEDGE, SKILLS AND EXPERIENCE REQUIRED 
============================================== 
 
 Five plus years of experience developing HTML front ends for cloud based, commercial applications
 Experince with moc ups designing workflows Bachelors or Masterâ€™s degree in Computer Science or related field
 Advanced knowledge and proficient expertise with HTML-based application development
 Web tooling stack including HTML components, JavaScript, CSS, AngularJS, Typescript, React, Bootstrap, etc.
 Experience with UX design patterns and Material Design guidelines
 Awareness of, and interest in, cutting-edge interface designs and industry trends (responsive Web design, mobile design patterns, etc.)
 Experience with desktop applications using C# and WPF; needed to help work with existing products that are not yet web-enabled 
